headline: Has Quanta Services Share Surge Outrun Its Growth Prospects in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether Quanta Services is still worth buying after such a huge run, or if the market has already priced in all the good news, this breakdown will help you assess whether the current price tag makes sense. The stock has climbed 2.4% over the last week, 4.1% over the last month, and 46.8% year to date, building on a 44.0% one year gain and a 582.4% return over five years that has clearly shifted how investors view its prospects and risk profile.
